code: // ------------------------------------------------------------------------ @Override public int hashCode() {     int code = 31 * address + state.hashCode().     return 31 * code + transition.hashCode(). }

@Override public boolean equals(Object obj) {     if (this == obj) {         return true.     } else if (obj == null || getClass() != obj.getClass()) {         return false.     } else {         final Alert that = (Alert) obj.         return this.address == that.address && this.transition == that.transition && this.state == that.state.     } }
@Override public String toString() {     return "ALERT " + Event.formatAddress(address) + " : " + state.name() + " -> " + transition.name(). }
